<br>
Everything can be tanked not using def?  Fighting in cod (tier 2 zone), I've tanked mobs that quad for 2k and proc a 3500 lifetap.  Defensive/Evasive not helping for that?<br>
<br>
Defensive kinda became obsolete with uber CH rotation and fights of more then 20 min.  That's not the case anymore.<br>
<br>
The &quot;crutches&quot; of which you talk might have been there at the end in luclin, but defensive is not a crutch holding us back anymore, it's a very powerfully tool that define the class.<br>
<br>
